## How to Use

1. Clone the repository:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/SYEDMUNEEEB/Adventure-responsive-landing-page.git
    ```

2. Open the `index.html` file in any browser to view the landing page.

## Customization

Feel free to customize the following:

- **Images**: Replace the default background images with your own adventure-themed images.
- **Text Content**: Modify the text sections to suit your content and branding.
- **Social Media Links**: Replace the social media links with your own social media profiles.
  
## Installation

If you'd like to modify the code, follow these simple installation steps:

1. Clone the repository to your local machine:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/SYEDMUNEEEB/Adventure-responsive-landing-page.git
    ```

2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```bash
    cd Adventure-responsive-landing-page
    ```

3. Open `index.html` in your browser to view the landing page.

